Height map of India showing geographic distribution of subterranean amphipods. Question mark (?) indicates collections of undescribed specimens of 
<taxonomicName id="DAD44D17FFD9FFDDD124F84DFD0F46B2" authorityName="Hertzog" authorityYear="1933" box="[569,675,1965,1987]" class="Malacostraca" family="Bogidiellidae" genus="Bogidiella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="405" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
